  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK399">
<l>tāmiṉ puṟuva tulakiṉ puṟakkaṇṭu </l>
<l>kāmuṟuvar kaṟṟaṟin tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learned will long (for more learning), when they see that while it gives pleasure to themselves, the world also derives pleasure from it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
